headline: Data & Business Process Services Stocks Q3 Earnings: Broadridge (NYSE:BR) Best of the Bunch
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q3. Today, we are looking at data & business process services stocks, starting with Broadridge (NYSE:BR).
